➜“品悟西游·致敬经典”读书感悟分享活动如期举办
http://www.sohu.com/a/425585381_606288	3738
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201018/d6fd671247814f62bb656427d231e555.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>西游记剧照。（资料图）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201018/26a6be87cd5a425383c6a0b2b019a81a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>“品悟西游·致敬经典”读书感悟分享活动现场。（西安安多素食餐饮供图）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201018/514d1d7b6e1a44c3a9d5a4909821f244.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
